'''東突厥斯坦流亡政府'''（{{ug|شەرقىي تۈركىستان سۈرگۈندى ھۆكۈمىتى|lat=Sherqiy Türkistan Sürgündi Hökümiti}}）是一個以議會為基礎的[[流亡政府|流亡政府]]，由[[維吾爾族|維吾爾族]]、[[哈薩克族|哈薩克族]]和來自[[東突厥斯坦|東突厥斯坦]]（[[新疆|新疆]]）的其他民族所建立，其總部設在[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]。該組織聲稱其是在國際舞台上代表東突厥斯坦及其人民的唯一機構。<ref>{{cite web |title=About the ETGE |url=https://east-turkistan.net/about-the-etge/ |website=East Turkistan Government in Exile |access-date=2021-03-10 |archive-date=2020-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116025803/https://east-turkistan.net/about-the-etge/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Bovingdon">{{cite book |last1=Bovingon |first1=Gardner |title=The Uyghurs: Strangers in their own land |date=2010 |publisher=Columbia University Press |location=New York |isbn=9780231519410 |page=150 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NrtIa77Sj2IC&q=September+14,+2004+East+Turkistan+exile+government&pg=PA150 |access-date=2020-05-11 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511224834/https://books.google.com/books?id=NrtIa77Sj2IC&q=September+14%2C+2004+East+Turkistan+exile+government&pg=PA150 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

儘管東突流亡政府在[[美國國會大廈|美國國會大廈]]HC-6室宣佈成立，但美國尚未承認東突流亡政府及其所聲稱的領土。<ref>{{cite book |last1=Bovingdon |first1=Gardner |title=The Uyghurs: Strangers in Their Own Land |date=2010 |publisher=Columbia University Press |location=New York |isbn=9780231519410 |pages=150, 280 |url=https://www.google.com/books/edition/The_Uyghurs/NrtIa77Sj2IC?hl=en&gbpv=1&dq=East+turkistan+Government+in+Exile+Hc-6&pg=PA150&printsec=frontcover |access-date=2021-04-11 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511224828/https://www.google.com/books/edition/The_Uyghurs/NrtIa77Sj2IC?hl=en&gbpv=1&dq=East+turkistan+Government+in+Exile+Hc-6&pg=PA150&printsec=frontcover |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://2001-2009.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2004/38594.htm |title=China - No Recognition of Any East Turkestan Government in Exile (Taken Question) |author=<!--Not stated--> |date=2004-11-22 |website=U.S. Department of State |publisher=U.S. Department of State |quote=The U.S. Government does not recognize any East Turkestan government-in-exile, nor do we provide support for any such entity. |access-date=2021-04-28 |archive-date=2017-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117170310/https://2001-2009.state.gov/r/pa/prs/ps/2004/38594.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>自2004年9月以來，[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]一直對東突流亡政府的成立表示強烈反對。<ref>{{cite news |title=China Protests Establishment of Uighur Government-in-Exile in Washington |url=https://www.voanews.com/archive/china-protests-establishment-uighur-government-exile-washington-2004-09-21 |access-date=2020-06-14 |publisher=Voice of America |date=2004-09-21 |archive-date=2020-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617032226/https://www.voanews.com/archive/china-protests-establishment-uighur-government-exile-washington-2004-09-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 地位 ==
{{see also|東突厥斯坦獨立運動}}
東突厥斯坦一直由中華人民共和國所控制。東突流亡政府認為這是非法的[[軍事佔領|軍事佔領]]。東突流亡政府的立场是「東突厥斯坦與其人民有著漫長的獨立歷史」。<ref>{{cite web |title=Uyghurs urge US Congress to recognize East Turkistan as an Occupied Country |url=https://east-turkistan.net/uyghurs-urge-us-congress-to-recognize-east-turkistan-as-an-occupied-country/ |website=East Turkistan Government in Exile |accessdate=2020-06-14 |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614201802/https://east-turkistan.net/uyghurs-urge-us-congress-to-recognize-east-turkistan-as-an-occupied-country/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>東突流亡政府官員並不認為自己是「分離主義者」，他們表示「你不能從不屬於你的東西中分離出來」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Fink |first1=Kathryn |title=‘For Their Own Good’: The Detention Of Muslim Ethnic Groups In China |url=https://the1a.org/segments/2019-12-23-uighurs/ |accessdate=2020-06-14 |agency=National Public Radio |date=2019-12-23 |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614235535/https://the1a.org/segments/2019-12-23-uighurs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>而中華人民共和國認為，中國在1949年就已經「[[新疆和平解放|和平解放新疆]]」。該地區「早就是中國的一部分」。<ref>{{cite news |title=China issues white paper on historical matters concerning Xinjiang |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2019-07/21/c_138244624.htm |access-date=2020-06-14 |agency=Xinhua News |publisher=State Council Information Office |date=2019-07-21 |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614235752/http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2019-07/21/c_138244624.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

東突流亡政府稱自己是实行民主選舉和議會制度的流亡政府，訴求是結束「中國對東突厥斯坦的佔領和殖民」。中國稱東突厥斯坦為[[新疆維吾爾自治區|新疆維吾爾自治區]]，而東突流亡政府則要求「恢復東突厥斯坦的獨立」，並將採取[[自由民主制|民主的]][[議會共和制|議會共和制]]的形式，保護該地區所有人的[[公民自由|公民自由]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=Government Policy Statement |url=https://east-turkistan.net/about-the-etge/ |website=East Turkistan Government in Exile |access-date=2020-05-11 |archive-date=2020-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116025803/https://east-turkistan.net/about-the-etge/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>自成立以來，東突流亡政府已經於2004年、2006年、2008年、2009年、2011年、2013年、2015年和2019年召開了八次大會。政府總部設在華盛頓特區，那里居住著大量的維吾爾族，但其成員分佈在十幾個國家。<ref>{{cite news |title=China Protests Establishment of Uighur Government-in-Exile in Washington - 2004-09-21 |url=https://www.voanews.com/archive/china-protests-establishment-uighur-government-exile-washington-2004-09-21 |access-date=2020-05-11 |publisher=Voice of America |date=2004-10-21 |archive-date=2020-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617032226/https://www.voanews.com/archive/china-protests-establishment-uighur-government-exile-washington-2004-09-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 形成 ==
2004年初，東突厥斯坦民族中心内部在選擇獨立或自治的問題上發生了分歧，並進一步導致了[[世界維吾爾代表大會|世界維吾爾代表大會]]和東突流亡政府的形成。前者拒絕獨立主張自治，而後者則拒絕自治主張獨立。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Shichor |first1=Yitzhak |title=Changing the Guard at the World Uyghur Congress |journal=China Brief |date=2006-12-19 |volume=6 |issue=25 |url=https://jamestown.org/program/changing-the-guard-at-the-world-uyghur-congress-3/ |access-date=2021-03-26 |archive-date=2021-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418221420/https://jamestown.org/program/changing-the-guard-at-the-world-uyghur-congress-3/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2004年9月14日，在[[安瓦爾·玉素甫·圖拉尼|安瓦爾·玉素甫·圖拉尼]]的領導下，全球東突厥斯坦社區成員在美國國會大廈HC-6室正式宣布東突厥斯坦流亡政府成立。<ref>{{cite news |title=Voice of America Report on Chinese Opposition of ETGIE |url=https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Voice_of_America_Report_on_Chinese_Opposition_of_ETGIE.ogg |agency=Voice of America News |date=2004-09-14 |accessdate=2021-04-28 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511224831/https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Voice_of_America_Report_on_Chinese_Opposition_of_ETGIE.ogg |dead-url=no }}</ref>阿赫马特·伊甘巴迪被與會代表選為總統，他曾是1992年成立的東突厥斯坦國際大會的首任主席。而圖拉尼則當選總理。<ref name="Bovingdon" />

