=== 總理 ===
2019年11月11日，在第八屆[[東突厥斯坦流亡政府大會|東突厥斯坦流亡政府大會]]上，年輕的維吾爾族獨立活動人士、[[東突厥斯坦民族覺醒運動|東突厥斯坦民族覺醒運動]]創始人[[薩利赫·胡達亞爾|薩利赫·胡達亞爾]]被選為東突流亡政府的第四任總理。<ref>{{cite web |last1=ETGE |title=Prime Minister |url=https://east-turkistan.net/prime-minister/ |website=East Turkistan Government in Exile |access-date=2021-01-25 |archive-date=2019-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215035420/https://east-turkistan.net/prime-minister/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Shukla |first1=Manish |title=East Turkistan Government in Exile Prime Minister Salih Hudayar wishes India on Independence Day |url=https://zeenews.india.com/india/east-turkistan-government-in-exile-prime-minister-salih-hudayar-wishes-india-on-independence-day-2303089.html |access-date=2021-01-25 |agency=Zee News |date=2020-08-16 |archive-date=2020-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822154938/https://zeenews.india.com/india/east-turkistan-government-in-exile-prime-minister-salih-hudayar-wishes-india-on-independence-day-2303089.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

