== 活動 ==
東突流亡政府開展了廣泛的宣傳活動，旨在提高人們對東突厥斯坦各民族人權狀況的認識，包括維吾爾族、哈薩克族、[[吉爾吉斯族|吉爾吉斯族]]等。該政府明確主張恢復東突厥斯坦的獨立，其成員主要活躍於美國國會、加拿大政府、歐盟成員國、北約、日本和印度。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Hatch |first1=Caleb |title=Prime Minister Salih Hudayar on China |url=https://www.wowo.com/prime-minister-salih-hudayar-on-china/ |access-date=2020-06-14 |agency=News/Talk WOWO 1190 AM/107.5 FM |date=2020-06-03 |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614235937/https://www.wowo.com/prime-minister-salih-hudayar-on-china/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=MSO called webinar on East Turkistan atrocities |url=https://timesheadline.com/india/mso-called-webinar-on-east-turkistan-atrocities-47041.html |access-date=2020-06-14 |agency=Times Headline |date=2020-06-04 |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614201804/https://timesheadline.com/india/mso-called-webinar-on-east-turkistan-atrocities-47041.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年3月，在新當選的胡達亞爾總理的領導下，東突流亡政府和東突厥斯坦社區成員會見了美國眾議員[[泰德·約霍|泰德·約霍]]，並邀請他就東突厥斯坦問題在美國眾議院發表演講。約霍稱東突厥斯坦是一個「被佔領的國家」，並譴責中國對維吾爾族、哈薩克族、吉爾吉斯族和其他突厥民族進行種族滅絕。<ref name="Yoho">{{cite web |title=Congressman Yoho Tweet |last1=Ted |first1=Yoho |url=https://twitter.com/reptedyoho/status/1237463307260514305 |via=Twitter |access-date=2020-05-11 |archive-date=2020-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200310214401/https://twitter.com/reptedyoho/status/1237463307260514305 |dead-url=no }}{{Primary source inline|date=2021-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Congressman Ted Yoho's Speech on China's Oppression in East Turkistan |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-8_0fkiLE-I |via=YouTube |publisher=CSPAN |access-date=2020-05-11 |archive-date=2020-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626181537/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-8_0fkiLE-I |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Congress |first1=US |title=House of Representatives |journal=Congressional Record: Proceedings and Debates of the 116th Congress, Second Session |date=2020-03-11 |volume=166 |issue=47 |page=1815 |url=https://www.congress.gov/116/crec/2020/03/11/CREC-2020-03-11.pdf |access-date=2020-05-11 |archive-date=2020-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200617055501/https://www.congress.gov/116/crec/2020/03/11/CREC-2020-03-11.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

東突流亡政府本無意偏向任何黨派，但在東突厥斯坦問題上得到了[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]更多的支持。而總理則在保守派媒體上不定期露面，包括在[[史蒂夫·班農|史蒂夫·班農]]的作戰室做客。<ref name="Yoho" /><ref>{{cite news |title=How the coronavirus impacts religious minorities encountering human rights abuses in China |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ekdBA9KlHo&t=2s |access-date=2020-06-14 |agency=One America News Network |date=2020-03-24 |archive-date=2020-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200628000851/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ekdBA9KlHo&feature=emb_title |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Persecution of Ehtnic Minorities in China - Salih Hudayar |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wyC04HIfMHA |access-date=2020-06-14 |agency=Dove Tv |date=2020-03-24 |archive-date=2020-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706190000/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wyC04HIfMHA |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Gary |first1=Lane |title=China Appointed to UN Human Rights Council as it forces Uyghurs into Slave Labor |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XqHZdYu8IHo |access-date=2020-06-14 |agency=Christian Broadcasting Network |date=2020-04-09 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929072621/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XqHZdYu8IHo |dead-url=no }}</ref>2019年11月，[[美國國家安全會議|美國國家安全會議]]前戰略計劃總監，退休的[[美國空軍|美國空軍]]准將[[羅伯特·斯伯丁|羅伯特·斯伯丁]]、[[美國國防部|美國國防部]]前中國事務主任約瑟夫·博斯科，和其他政局分析專家参加了東突流亡政府第八屆大會，並發表了講話。<ref>{{cite web |title=Summary of the ETGE's 8th General Assembly (November 10–12) |url=https://east-turkistan.net/summary-of-the-etges-8th-general-assembly-november-10-12/ |website=East Turkistan Government in Exile |access-date=2020-06-14 |archive-date=2019-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215035255/https://east-turkistan.net/summary-of-the-etges-8th-general-assembly-november-10-12/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年6月，東突流亡政府對反對「[[中華帝國主義|中華帝國主義]]」的組織表示支持，包括許多維吾爾族，[[滿族|滿族]]和[[藏族|藏族]]的獨立運動團體，並且致函[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]，[[歐洲聯盟理事會|歐洲聯盟理事會]]，以及印度、日本和英國的外交部長。政府在信中表示拒絕「中國的佔領」，並呼籲「國際社會幫助各民族達成一項民主決議，給予東突厥斯坦、[[滿洲|滿洲]]、[[南蒙古|南蒙古]]和[[西藏|西藏]]完全的民族獨立。」<ref>{{cite web |title=Open Letter Opposing China's Imperialism in East Turkistan, Manchuria, South Mongolia, and Tibet |url=https://east-turkistan.net/open-letter-opposing-chinas-imperialism-in-east-turkistan-manchuria-south-mongolia-and-tibet/ |website=East Turkistan Government in Exile |access-date=2020-06-14 |archive-date=2020-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615001807/https://east-turkistan.net/open-letter-opposing-chinas-imperialism-in-east-turkistan-manchuria-south-mongolia-and-tibet/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

據報導，2020年7月6日，「東突厥斯坦流亡政府」和「東突厥斯坦民族覺醒運動」向[[國際刑事法院|國際刑事法院]]起訴包括[[習近平|習近平]]在內的中華人民共和國現任和前任中國官員。

東突流亡政府讚揚了《[[維吾爾人權政策法案|維吾爾人權政策法案]]》的通過，該法案要求美國政府各機構報告[[新疆人權問題|新疆人權問題]]。隨後政府也向美國總統[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]和美國國會表示了感謝。東突流亡政府表示，「我們希望這將是東突厥斯坦恢復自由和獨立的第一步。」<ref>{{cite news |last1=Sheperd |first1=Josh |title=President Trump Signs Law to Halt China's Egregious Human Rights Abuses |url=https://stream.org/trump-uyghur-human-rights-policy-act/?fbclid=IwAR21TUjvLnMupMPOvhKnaU1AdxTUKGZwFDzY_xVRHIOCdU0Tz-UOCe9mLKk |access-date=2020-06-20 |agency=The Stream |date=2020-06-19 |archive-date=2020-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622002238/https://stream.org/trump-uyghur-human-rights-policy-act/?fbclid=IwAR21TUjvLnMupMPOvhKnaU1AdxTUKGZwFDzY_xVRHIOCdU0Tz-UOCe9mLKk |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Statement Thanking the United States for Passing & Signing the Uyghur Act |url=https://east-turkistan.net/statement-thanking-the-united-states-for-passing-signing-the-uyghur-act/ |website=East Turkistan Government in Exile |access-date=2020-06-20 |archive-date=2020-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706190039/https://east-turkistan.net/statement-thanking-the-united-states-for-passing-signing-the-uyghur-act/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年7月14日，東突流亡政府與64名加拿大國會議員和20個組織簽署聯合信，敦促加拿大總理[[賈斯汀·杜魯道|賈斯汀·杜魯道]]、副總理[[方慧蘭|方慧蘭]]和外交部長[[商鵬飛|商鵬飛]]制裁部分中國內地和香港官員，因為這些官員「對發生在西藏、香港和被佔領的東突厥斯坦的人權暴行負有直接責任」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Smith |first1=Marie-Danielle |title=60 MPs urge sanctions against Chinese officials |url=https://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/60-mps-urge-sanctions-against-chinese-officials/ |access-date=2020-07-24 |work=Maclean's |date=2020-07-14 |archive-date=2020-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724053444/https://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/60-mps-urge-sanctions-against-chinese-officials/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

