2020年7月6日，據《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》和《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》報導，東突流亡政府和東突民族覺醒運動向[[國際刑事法庭|國際刑事法庭]]提出訴訟請求，敦促其在數月內完成對中國官員的調查和起訴。起訴內容包括[[種族滅絕|種族滅絕]]等[[反人類罪行|反人類罪行]]。<ref name="nytimes.com">{{cite news |last1=Simons |first1=Marlise |title=Uighur Exiles Push for Court Case Accusing China of Genocide |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/06/world/asia/china-xinjiang-uighur-court.html |access-date=2020-07-24 |work=The New York Times |date=2020-07-06 |archive-date=2020-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710011145/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/07/06/world/asia/china-xinjiang-uighur-court.html/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="wsj.com">{{cite news |last1=Areddy |first1=James T. |title=Representatives of China's Uighurs File Evidence to International Criminal Court |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/representatives-of-chinas-uighurs-file-evidence-to-international-criminal-court-11594078290 |access-date=2020-07-24 |work=The Wall Street Journal |date=2020-07-06 |archive-date=2020-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200721155706/https://www.wsj.com/articles/representatives-of-chinas-uighurs-file-evidence-to-international-criminal-court-11594078290 |dead-url=no }}</ref>這是首次有組織試圖利用國際法律平台，就嚴重侵犯東突厥斯坦穆斯林的人權向中國提出指控。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Sewell |first1=Tia |title=Unpacking the Recent Uighur ICC Complaint Against Chinese Leaders |url=https://www.lawfareblog.com/unpacking-recent-uighur-icc-complaint-against-chinese-leaders |access-date=2020-07-24 |agency=Lawfare |date=2020-07-21 |archive-date=2020-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724012808/https://www.lawfareblog.com/unpacking-recent-uighur-icc-complaint-against-chinese-leaders |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Smith |first1=Samuel |title=ICC urged to investigate Chinese leaders for genocide abuses against Uighur Muslims |url=https://www.christianpost.com/news/icc-urged-to-investigate-chinese-leaders-for-genocide-abuses-against-uighur-muslims.html |access-date=2020-07-24 |work=The Christian Post |date=2020-07-10 |archive-date=2020-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725055720/https://www.christianpost.com/news/icc-urged-to-investigate-chinese-leaders-for-genocide-abuses-against-uighur-muslims.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>這份長達80頁的訴狀包括一份名單，其中有30多位中國高級官員的名字，[[中共中央總書記|中共中央總書記]]習近平也在其中。東突流亡政府認為習近平應對這些暴行負責。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bajwa |first1=Muzaffar Ahmad Noori |title=Uyghur Muslims finally dragged Chinese Communist Party to ICC for their crimes against humanity |url=https://www.easternherald.com/religion/uyghur-muslims-icc-china-73560/ |access-date=2020-07-24 |work=The Eastern Herald |date=2020-07-07 |archive-date=2020-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724032600/https://easternherald.com/religion/uyghur-muslims-icc-china-73560/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Exiled Uighurs approach International Criminal Court seeking justice against China |url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/world/2020/jul/07/exiled-uighurs-approach-international-criminal-court-seeking-justice-against-china-2166586.html |access-date=2020-07-24 |work=The New Indian Express |publisher=ANI |date=2020-07-07 |archive-date=2020-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724031448/https://www.newindianexpress.com/world/2020/jul/07/exiled-uighurs-approach-international-criminal-court-seeking-justice-against-china-2166586.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>第二天，東突流亡政府和東突厥斯坦民族覺醒運動在華盛頓特區和海牙舉行了在線新聞發布會。<ref>{{cite web|last=East Turkistan Government-in-Exile|title=Uyghur Genocide & Crimes Against Humanity ICC Complaint|url=https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Nkz429uJibg|via=YouTube|publisher=East Turkistan Government in Exile|access-date=2021-04-28|archive-date=2021-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511224821/https://www.youtube.com/watch?app=desktop&v=Nkz429uJibg|dead-url=no}}</ref>胡達亞爾向[[自由亞洲電台|自由亞洲電台]]華語頻道表示，「我們被中國和中共壓迫的如此之久，遭受的苦難如此之多，對我們人民的種族滅絕不能再被忽視了。」<ref>{{cite news |last1=Tang |first1=Jane |title=Uyghur Exile Groups Seek International Criminal Court Probe of Chinese Officials For 'Genocide' |url=https://www.rfa.org/english/news/uyghur/icc-07152020134752.html |access-date=2020-07-24 |agency=Radio Free Asia |date=2020-07-15 |archive-date=2020-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724012313/https://www.rfa.org/english/news/uyghur/icc-07152020134752.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

