=== 反「東伊運」污名化 ===
東突流亡政府是唯一一個公開主張將「[[東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動|東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動]]」從恐怖組織名單中除名的維吾爾族組織。他們認為東伊運是中國捏造的，目的是「把維吾爾族錯誤地描繪成恐怖分子」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Revi |first1=Amitabh P. |title=Disastrous Mistake Not To Stay In India, Delhi Opened Doors To Uyghurs Fleeing China: 'East Turkistan PM In Exile' |url=https://stratnewsglobal.com/china/disastrous-mistake-not-to-stay-in-india-delhi-opened-doors-to-uyghurs-fleeing-china-east-turkistan-pm-in-exile/ |access-date=2021-01-25 |agency=StratNews Global |date=2020-09-08 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130120209/https://stratnewsglobal.com/china/disastrous-mistake-not-to-stay-in-india-delhi-opened-doors-to-uyghurs-fleeing-china-east-turkistan-pm-in-exile/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=East Turkistan has never been part of China - Salih Hudayar |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BoxS1HYergI |via=YouTube |publisher=India Narrative |access-date=2021-01-25 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129223557/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BoxS1HYergI |dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年9月11日，東突流亡政府召開新聞發布會，譴責「東伊運」是「中國捏造」，並宣稱「21世紀恐怖主義的最大受害者是東突厥斯坦及其人民」。<ref>{{cite web |last1=ETGE |title=The Greatest Victims of Terrorism In The 21st Century Are East Turkistan And Its People |url=https://east-turkistan.net/the-biggest-victims-of-terrorism-in-the-21st-century-are-east-turkistan-and-its-people/ |website=East Turkistan Government in Exile |access-date=2021-01-25 |archive-date=2021-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201120849/https://east-turkistan.net/the-biggest-victims-of-terrorism-in-the-21st-century-are-east-turkistan-and-its-people/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年10月，時任美國國務卿[[邁克·蓬佩奧|邁克·蓬佩奧]]下令將東伊運從[[美國國務院公佈的外國恐怖組織名單|美國國務院公佈的外國恐怖組織名單]]中除名。該指令於2020年11月5日公佈，美國國務院之所以做出這一決定，是因為「十多年來，沒有可信證據表明東伊運仍然存在」。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Kashgarian |first1=Asim |title=Uighur Diaspora Hails Removal of ETIM From US Terror List |url=https://www.voanews.com/extremism-watch/uighur-diaspora-hails-removal-etim-us-terror-list |access-date=2021-01-25 |publisher=Voice of America |date=2020-12-25 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120225212/https://www.voanews.com/extremism-watch/uighur-diaspora-hails-removal-etim-us-terror-list |dead-url=no }}</ref>

東突流亡政府對美國政府將東伊運從恐怖組織名單中除名表示感謝，並敦促其他國家也做出同樣決定。<ref name="aninews.in">{{cite news |title=East Turkistan Government-in-Exile urges ICC to recognise China's atrocities against Uyghurs |url=https://www.aninews.in/news/world/asia/east-turkistan-government-in-exile-urges-icc-to-recognise-chinas-atrocities-against-uyghurs20201111141357/ |access-date=2021-01-25 |agency=ANI |date=2020-11-11 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129151642/https://www.aninews.in/news/world/asia/east-turkistan-government-in-exile-urges-icc-to-recognise-chinas-atrocities-against-uyghurs20201111141357/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>而中方則指責美國採取雙重標準。<ref name="SC">{{cite web |url=https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3108846/china-accuses-us-double-standards-it-drops-etim-terrorism-list |title=China accuses US of double standards as it drops ETIM from terrorism list |date=2020-11-06 |work=[[South_China_Morning_Post|South China Morning Post]] |access-date=2021-02-21 |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106141251/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3108846/china-accuses-us-double-standards-it-drops-etim-terrorism-list |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 認定中國實施種族滅絕 ===
