r Liu He's attention as his motorcade whizzes past |url=https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3046296/chinese-protesters-angle-liu-hes-attention-his-motorcade |access-date=2021-01-25 |work=South China Morning Post |date=2020-01-16 |archive-date=2021-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428124041/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3046296/chinese-protesters-angle-liu-hes-attention-his-motorcade |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Pasquini |first1=Elaine |title=East Turkistan Uyghurs Fear Annihilation by China |journal=Washington Report on Middle East Affairs |date=2020-12 |issue=November/December 2020 |page=52 |url=https://www.wrmea.org/human-rights/east-turkistan-uyghurs-fear-annihilation-by-china.html |access-date=2021-01-25 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130143107/https://www.wrmea.org/human-rights/east-turkistan-uyghurs-fear-annihilation-by-china.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=US Needs To Realise Atrocities On Uyghurs By China Is Nothing Less Than Genocide: East Turkistan Govt In Exile |url=http://www.businessworld.in/article/US-needs-to-realise-atrocities-on-Uyghurs-by-China-is-nothing-less-than-genocide-East-Turkistan-govt-in-exile/12-10-2020-330564/ |access-date=2021-01-25 |agency=ANI |date=2020-10-12 |archive-date=2021-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127134403/http://www.businessworld.in/article/US-needs-to-realise-atrocities-on-Uyghurs-by-China-is-nothing-less-than-genocide-East-Turkistan-govt-in-exile/12-10-2020-330564/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年10月，東突流亡政府成功說服加拿大議會承認中國政府實施種族滅絕，其後東突流亡政府對此表示感謝，並敦促加拿大政府也正式承認這一點。<ref name="aninews.in"/>之後他們還成功遊說美國參議院提出種族滅絕決議，並敦促美國政府承認種族滅絕。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Burnett |first1=Rebecca |title=Prime minister condemns Muslims' lack of support for imprisoned Uyghurs |url=https://www.localdvm.com/news/international/prime-minister-condemns-muslims-lack-of-support-for-imprisoned-uyghurs/ |access-date=2021-01-25 |publisher=WDVM |date=2020-11-10 |archive-date=2021-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212144501/https://www.localdvm.com/news/international/prime-minister-condemns-muslims-lack-of-support-for-imprisoned-uyghurs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Burnett |first1=Rebecca |title=East Turkistan Government in Exile protests outside Capitol on International Human Rights Day |url=https://www.localdvm.com/news/washington-dc/east-turkistan-government-in-exile-protests-outside-capitol-on-international-human-rights-day/ |access-date=2021-01-25 |publisher=WDVM |date=2020-12-10 |archive-date=2021-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218023115/https://www.localdvm.com/news/washington-dc/east-turkistan-government-in-exile-protests-outside-capitol-on-international-human-rights-day/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

